1943;;It's That Man Again;;British;;Walter Forde;;Tommy Handley, Greta Gynt;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/It%27s_That_Man_Again_(film);;The disreputable mayor (Tommy Handley) of small town Foaming-at-the-Mouth gambles the civic accounts and wins a bombed out local theatre. He steals the rights to a new play which he stages in an attempt to save the financial situation. However, local drama students he has cheated turn up and try to ruin the show.